### 주문 생성
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: password123

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 },
    { "productId": 3, "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### 주문 생성 (쿠폰 적용)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: password123

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 }
  ],
  "couponId": 1
}

### 내 주문 목록 조회 (날짜 필터)
GET {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/orders?startAt=2026-01-01&endAt=2026-12-31
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: password123

### 주문 상세 조회
GET {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/orders/1
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: password123
